race.comment: LE TROY (2) settled too far back at Lenora in stronger but spiked his figures beaten a nose at Junction prior. That's good form, and he can bounce back at this level. BLOWIN' SMOKE (1) went well at Geraldton and then got off the mark over 1200m at Leonora. Fitter again and a decent chance to go back-to-back. GINGER JIVE (3) has placed her last two in Open 3s at Leonora and tumbles in weight. Has a nice gate and deserves consideration. LENNOX LASS (5) settled back in the same race and didn't get warm. Showed improvement prior and maps better today with a 2kg claimer engaged. Won't be that far away.
